item.title: Any rich here can give me head start?
item.dc:creator: @davidude36 Brolapse
item.description:
@davidude36 wrote:

ok get a wc axe (woodcutting axe) hopefully bronze, now if you dont have one, commit suicide, run out of the castle nd kill sum men, grab their money and walk a little south east of the castle, their should be a couple of houses, hopefully you will find an axe shop, talk to the dude and buy an axe, if you dont have enough money kill some more dudes… now you have an axe, right? if you dont… ure screwed, i take it your woodcutting level is 1, well go find a normal “tree” and click on it, you should start chopping away and eventually get a log, keep doing this repeatedly untill you get level 15 woodcutting, then find around runescape “oak” trees, cut them and maybe even sell them, but i wouldnt advise selling them, best to drop them. ok now keep cutting oaks/trees untill you are level 30 woodcutting, go west of the castle you start in across the swamp untill you find a bank, below the bank are willow trees, cut them and bank them, when you have about 1k willow logs (1000) you can sell them at about 30-45gp each, 30gp X 1000 = 30k (30,000) their you have made money and gotten woodcutting levels, i advise u continue doing this untill level 60 woodcutting then find some “yew” trees, cut and bank their logs as they sell at 300gp each! also another tip is as you level you can use better wood cutting axes… its best to use rune if u can, they sell for 20k each or under (20,000gp)
ok so i hope this helped you as it just wasted bout 10 minutes of my time… and please no more asking for phree m00n3y pl0x.
